Package graph

Class AdjMatrixDiGraph<T>

java.lang.Object
graph.AdjMatrixDiGraph<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
GraphADT<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
AdjMatrixGraph, WeightedAdjMatrixDiGraph
public class AdjMatrixDiGraph<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements GraphADT<T>
An implementation of the GraphADTinterface for a directed graph using an adjacency matrix to indicate the presence/absence of edges connecting vertices in the graph.
